# SplitSquad Project Overview

SplitSquad is a web application for splitting expenses and managing shared payments among groups of people. It allows users to create groups, add expenses, track who paid what, and calculate balances.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 with React 19
- TypeScript
- Supabase for backend database and authentication
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Shadcn UI components

